title: Here Is Your Complete List of Winners From the 2017 Golden Globes
text:
Jan. 8 2017 7:25 PM Here Is Your Complete List of Winners From the 2017 Golden Globes La La Land leads the pack for film with seven nominations. Dale Robinette/Lionsgate 
Can Deadpool topple La La Land ? Will The People v. O.J. Simpson repeat its Emmys triumph? And is this the year Netflix takes home the award for best drama TV series? Check back here throughout the night for all the latest winners. 
You can also read our critics on the night’s jokes, fashion, and more on Slate ’s Golden Globes live blog . Advertisement
